## Development Workflow
1. Feature planning → Document in SPECIFY.md
2. Implementation → Follow code standards
3. Testing → Unit + integration tests
4. Documentation → Update relevant docs
5. Deployment → CI/CD via GitHub Actions

## Security Guidelines
- Never commit API keys (use .env)
- Validate all inputs (Pydantic models)
- Implement rate limiting (15 req/min)
- Use HTTPS/TLS for all communications
- Sanitize user inputs (XSS prevention)

## Performance Requirements
- Page load: < 3s
- API response: < 5s (chat), < 10s (translation)
- Uptime: 99.5%
- Support: 100+ concurrent users

